HEADWORD: Refusion
<hw>Re*fu"sion</hw> <pr>(r?*f?"zh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>fusion</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
